{
  "stem": "24111.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A [NON-ENGLISH] is an official immigration document similar to an-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] certificate to go to Palestine or a quota number to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Bauer immediately sent him a [NON-ENGLISH] for my father, my mother, and the two children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we would have been able to emigrate from Vienna almost immediately, because in the meantime we made our passports, which were stamped with a large J, meaning Jew-- Jew-- Jew.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got also all the necessary travel documents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we even had the-- the ship tickets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember it was the HAPAG going from Hamburg to Montevideo and then Montevideo up the Parana to Asuncion in Paraguay.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But suddenly, something came up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It came that my father had, in Switzerland, in the little town of Wil, not far--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wil, W-E-- W-I-L, not far from St.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Gallen-- machineries producing [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] lace.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Swiss farmers, during the wintertime when the-- when they had very little work to do, produced lace on large, long, special machineries for him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, he had also money, Swiss money, in the-- in Swiss banks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He has-- he had machinery.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he had an-- a commerce between Switzerland and Austria.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when the Germans took the business away, they wanted this particular machinery, which was a very delicate and special piece of equipment, transferred from Switzerland, from Wil, to Austria.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And also, they wanted the Swiss franc, which were in Swiss banks, transferred to Austria.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they did allow only out of four passports two passports for emigration.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
